                              format="html"
                              scope="external"
                              class="- topic/xref ">41 U.S.C. 1708(e)(3)</xref>,
Minimum Response Time for Offers (see <xref href="5.203.dita#FAR_5_203"
                              base="i1120755"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">5.203</xref>).</p>
                  </li>
