            <li class="- topic/li ">
               <p class="- topic/p " id="d738e119">
                  <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(b)</ph> Certain
                  requirements of the following laws are not applicable to
                  executive agency contracts for the acquisition of commercial
                  products and commercial services: </p>
               <ol id="d711e174" class="- topic/ol ">
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p " id="d738e115">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(1)</ph>
                        <xref href="http://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=granuleid:USC-prelim-title22-section2593a&amp;num=0&amp;edition=prelim"
                              format="html"
                              scope="external"
                              class="- topic/xref ">22 U.S.C. 2593e</xref>, Requirement
for a certification under Measures Against Persons Involved in Activities
that Violate Arms Control Treaties or Agreements with the United
States (see <xref href="9.109.dita#FAR_9_109"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">9.109</xref>).</p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p " id="d738e125">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(2)</ph>
                        <xref href="http://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=granuleid%3AUSC-prelim-title40-chapter37&amp;saved=%7CZ3JhbnVsZWlkOlVTQy1wcmVsaW0tdGl0bGU0MC1jaGFwdGVyMzctZnJvbnQ%3D%7C%7C%7C0%7Cfalse%7Cprelim&amp;edition=prelim"
                              scope="external"
                              format="html"
                              class="- topic/xref ">40 U.S.C.chapter 37</xref>,
Requirement for a certificate and clause under the Contract Work
Hours and Safety Standards statute (see <xref href="22.305.dita#FAR_22_305"
                              base="i1098333"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">22.305</xref>).</p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p " id="d738e135">
                        <ph props="autonumber" class="- topic/ph ">(3)</ph>
                        <xref href="http://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=granuleid:USC-prelim-title41-section8703&amp;num=0&amp;edition=prelim"
