                              scope="external"
                              format="html"
                              class="- topic/xref ">8703</xref>, Requirement
for a clause and certain other requirements related to kickbacks
(see <xref href="3.502.dita#FAR_3_502"
                              base="i1124348"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">3.502</xref>).</p>
                  </li>
                  <li class="- topic/li ">
                     <p class="- topic/p " id="d738e148">
