                              scope="external"
                              format="html"
                              class="- topic/xref ">49 U.S.C.40118</xref>(g) is applicable to the acquisition of commercial services (see <xref href="47.405.dita#FAR_47_405"
                              base="i1070062"
                              outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                              class="- topic/xref ">47.405</xref>).
                     </p>
                  </li>
               </ol>
            </li>
            <li class="- topic/li ">
